Global Cellular Broadband Device and Module Market Insights
Cellular Broadband Device and Module Market size was valued at USD 45 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 78 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Cellular Broadband Device and Module Market Overview
The global cellular broadband device and module market is valued at approximately USD 18.5 billion in 2024 and is expected to reach around USD 32.5 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.8% during the forecast period. The increasing demand for high-speed data connectivity, rise in mobile internet usage, and growth of IoT devices are contributing significantly to the market expansion. The market is highly competitive, with key players developing advanced cellular modules to cater to the needs of various industries including automotive, healthcare, and smart homes. The growing adoption of 5G technology further propels market growth, creating new opportunities for market participants across the globe.

